10. avgift
11. miljarder
12. medlemskap
13. bidrag
14. nettobidragsgivare

There are 14 long words in the text.

Now, we can calculate the LIX readability score:

LIX = (72 / 5) + (14 / 72) x 100
LIX ≈ 40.6

However, the LIX formula typically uses three significant figures for the result.

LIX ≈ 40.6 ≈ 41

LIX = 41